text:

Post to Facebook Kate Upton goes topless for her third 'SI' Swimsuit Edition cover Upton was on the cover in 2012 and 2013.  //ftw.usatoday.com/2017/02/sports-illustrated-swimsuit-edition-cover-kate-upton-model-topless/   Kate Upton goes topless for her third 'SI' Swimsuit Edition cover adicjoseph 12:47   
Kate Upton. (Photo: USA TODAY Sports Images) 
Kate Upton is 24 years old and has as many banners as LeBron James. 
And for Upton's third year on the cover, Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Edition decided to honor the feat with a trifecta of its own. Upton will get three different covers in the 2017 edition, as was revealed Tuesday on Jimmy Kimmel Live. The 2017 SI Swimsuit Covers have been revealed. Welcome back, @KateUpton ! Follow the link for more photos and video https://t.co/4cszjybbVp pic.twitter.com/y7TguJdPVD â€” SI Swimsuit (@SI_Swimsuit) February 15, 2017 
The cover of the Swimsuit Edition is a closely guarded secret, and Upton hadn't even seen the images before Kimmel revealed them on TV. 
Upton also was on the cover in 2012 and 2013. Last year's edition featured three separate cover models: Ronda Rousey, Hailey Clauson and Ashley Graham. Read or Share this story: http://ftw.usatoday.com/2017/02/sports-illustrated-swimsuit-edition-cover-kate-upton-model-topless/ Most Popular
